{"title":"在我们的田野上","authors":["李绚"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":1,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们的田野上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李绚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗帘掀开天空的一角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风声渐紧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对闪电的逼视"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们泰然无畏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期待透雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞逝的光阴也难忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少次我们被洪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追赶得撤至堤头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少次我们被丰收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感动得热泪长流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们从不肯放弃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生养我们的这块土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们总爱用自信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织出绚烂的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们能承装比大地还大的荣幸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也能消溶比海洋更深的不幸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样，在我们的田野上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才不会喑哑亮丽的歌声"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}